Syntax: rent

This MUD does not use a rent system. There are no inn costs or storage fees
for logging out with items.

To leave the game safely, simply use:
  save    -- Saves your character to disk immediately.
  quit    -- Saves and disconnects you from the game.

Your equipment, gold, and character state are automatically saved when you
quit. There is no need to find an inn or pay rent.

See also: save quit
